-- Nintendo Reboots Wii Console
-- B y
-- 2012-06-05T03:33:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-05/nintendo-reboots-wii-console.html
Nintendo Co. is unveiling software 
for its upcoming Wii U console at this week's Electronic 
Entertainment Expo in Los Angeles. The console will combine TV 
screen action with a touch-screen controller. Nintendo is 
trying to attract gamers who have moved on from the Wii. 
(Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 00:58
 